SCIENTIFIC AND CLINICAL BREAKTHROUGHS


Advances in genomics and biotechnology are leading to breakthroughs in our fundamental understanding of diseases and the potential role of nutrition to better manage health. Through our external focus, research capabilities and network, we fuel our innovation pipeline of nutritional therapies..


Read more






ADVANCING THE ROLE OF THERAPEUTIC NUTRITION


The role of nutrition is entering a new stage of discovery and innovation – not just in addressing nutritional gaps but with potentially direct therapeutic impacts – that is changing the management of health and forging an increasingly integral role in the management of health across the human life cycle.



Read more


