BOOST® KID ESSENTIALS
BOOST® Kid Essentials™ Drink is a nutritionally complete drink for children ages 1-13.  A delicious snack or with a meal, BOOST® Kid Essentials™ gives kids the nutrition they need to help them grow.  Each serving contains 24 essential vitamins and minerals and 7 grams of protein, and a Kid-Approved Taste!  Available as ready-to-drink in chocolate and vanilla flavors, BOOST® Kid Essentials™ is a great way to supplement kids’ diets with extra nutrition.
