Impact


Impact is a clinically proven nutritional solution for the dietary management of major elective surgery patients, to improve clinical outcomes, and reduce postoperative complications and length of hospital stay. IMPACT formulation contains omega-3 fatty acids, arginine and nucleotides, and is suitable for use as a sole source of nutrition.
