For healthcare professionalsModulenA unique whole-protein, powdered formulation for use as a sole source of nutrition in the active phase of Crohn’s disease and for nutritional support during the remission phaseOptisourceA specially formulated vitamin and mineral supplement for use after malabsorptive bariatric surgeryVitafloVitaflo is at the forefront of developing innovative specialized medical foods for Metabolic Disorders, Nutrition Support and other areas of disease specific nutritionPeptamenA family of products offering well-tolerated, complete nutrition intended for the dietary management of patients with compromised or impaired GI functionMeriteneA family of products that addresses the needs of the body as it ages: from fatigue and decrease of muscle mass, to increased need of fiber supplementation and moreImpactA clinically proven specialist enteral feed for critically ill patients pre- and post-surgery or following traumaNovasourceNutritionally complete products appropriate for general nutritional support and the dietary management of diarrhea in adults receiving enteral nutritionDiabetisource ACAn advanced-control tube feed designed specifically to meet the unique nutritional needs of patients with diabetes and stress-induced hyperglycemiaCompatThe Compat® range of medical devices includes enteral feeding pumps and gravity administration sets, enteral access feeding tubes and a variety of accessories for both adult and pediatric patient populations.BoostA great-tasting nutritional supplement that provides all the nutrients needed for individuals who are not getting the right amount from their dietIsosourceA family of products composed of formulas that are intended for the dietary management of undernourished patients or those at risk of malnutritionOptifastA comprehensive, medically monitored, weight-management program that combines medical supervision, nutritionally complete meal replacement products and behavioral elementsResourceA wide range of product